Localization.AdminAnonymFoldersDescription:
amafolda Kubhala ngekuhlanganyela / amafayela - Yilezi amafolda / amafayela ukuthi asidingi ukuqinisekiswa lomsebenzisi *, lokho kusho ukuthi ayatholakala yazo zonke izivakashi * (uma une isixhumanisi). Bonke abasebenzisi kungadala amafolda enjalo / amafayela kusuka imenyu "Yabelana → Dala isixhumanisi yomphakathi". Nokho, amafolda okwabelwana ingase ibe izimvume limited: ukulayisha, ukulandwa, amafayela / amafolda ohlwini. Ngezansi ithebula izixhumanisi abelwe / amafayela adalwe abasebenzisi. Ukuze usebenze links umphakathi isici ngokunembile qiniseka ukuthi bokudla \ Anonymousdownload.ashx ivumela ukufinyelela engaziwa ku IIS. Ungase uhlole le ekhasini Diagnostics . Qiniseka ukuthi i-akhawunti yomsebenzisi engaziwa ababelwe kuwo bokudla \ Anonymousdownload.ashx ine NTFS Ukufundwa / lokubhala izimvume for abelwe / amafayela
